                    <div class="Item-Body">
                        <div class="Message userContent">
                            <p>Could you please pick a different last name to go by in our unit? We currently have someone in the unit with your lastname, and this will avoid confusion. Please reply to this thread with your desired new last name, and your application will be processed.</p>

<p>Also can you please tell us more about your Arma 2 experience? Under what name(s) you played, what rank(s) you held, and why you left that unit? Please use the below format:<br />
<code>| Unit | Game | Name | Rank | Reason for leaving |</code></p>

<p>Finally, before your application can be processed you'll need to confirm your selected preferred time.</p>

<p>We have two options for incoming members:<br />
(A) Attend 1 week of Basic Training at 7pm EST/Midnight GMT<br />
(B) Attend 1 week of Basic Training at 2pm EST/7pm GMT</p>

<p><em>Next Basic Training for Option A is scheduled for March 13 - 17.<br />
Next Basic Training for Option B is scheduled for March 06 - 10.</em></p>

<p>After you graduate Basic Training, you will then be assigned to a squad. There are similar options with that:<br />
(A) A squad which drills at around 8pm EST/1am GMT<br />
(B) A squad which drills at around 3pm EST/8pm GMT</p>
                        </div>
